\s1 \tl M'lakhim Alef\tl* / 1 King 7:51-8:21 (A); 7:40-50 (S)
\s1 \tl B'rit Hadashah\tl* ·New Covenant·: John 6:1-71
\b
\b
\s1 \tl Chazak, chazak v'nitchazek!\tl* ·Be Strong, be strong, and let us show ourselves courageous!· (2 Samuel 10:12)
\b
